<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>DevOps on Miya</title><link>https://tuobaling.github.io/categories/devops/</link><description>Recent content in DevOps on Miya</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-TW</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://tuobaling.github.io/categories/devops/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Hugo + Notion + Github Action 踩坑記錄 v1</title><link>https://tuobaling.github.io/blog/hugo-notion-github-action-log/</link><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://tuobaling.github.io/blog/hugo-notion-github-action-log/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="專案"&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%b0%88%e6%a1%88" class="md-heading-anchor"&gt;
 專案：
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a
 href="https://github.com/tuobaling/tuobaling.github.io/"
 target="_blank" rel="noopener"
 class="md-link"
&gt;
 https://github.com/tuobaling/tuobaling.github.io/
&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="踩坑"&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%b8%a9%e5%9d%91" class="md-heading-anchor"&gt;
 踩坑：
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;hugo 編譯完的public 要跟source code不同repository，否則部署完之後只會看到ReadMe.md&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;建立hugo.yaml 自動部署檔的時候，要改用gh-pages、github person access token再加上github 帳號才能做到跨repo push&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一定要在本機先裝好hugo並打包好，才能在本機建置確認站台內容是否有問題&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 id="建立步驟"&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%bb%ba%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a5%e9%a9%9f" class="md-heading-anchor"&gt;
 建立步驟：
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本倉庫以 Hugo + Minimal Black 主題建置 &lt;code&gt;{username}.github.io&lt;/code&gt; 靜態網站。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如需英文版導覽，請參考 &lt;a
 href="https://www.notion.so/README.md"
 target="_blank" rel="noopener"
 class="md-link"
&gt;
 README.md
&lt;/a&gt;
。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="資料夾架構"&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%b3%87%e6%96%99%e5%a4%be%e6%9e%b6%e6%a7%8b" class="md-heading-anchor"&gt;
 資料夾架構
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="mb-codeblock" id="cb-5feceb66" data-lang="plain"&gt;
 
 &lt;div class="mb-codeblock-header"&gt;
 &lt;div class="mb-codeblock-left"&gt;
 &lt;span class="mb-codeblock-badge"&gt;
 PLAIN
 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

 &lt;div class="mb-codeblock-actions"&gt;&lt;button class="mb-action-btn mb-collapse-btn" data-collapsed="false" aria-label="Collapse code"&gt;
 &lt;i class="fas fa-compress-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
 &lt;span&gt;Collapse&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/button&gt;&lt;button class="mb-action-btn mb-copy-btn" aria-label="Copy code"&gt;
 &lt;i class="fas fa-copy"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
 &lt;span&gt;Copy&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;

 
 &lt;div 
 class="mb-codeblock-content" 
 data-state="expanded"
 &gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-plain" data-lang="plain"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── archetypes/ - Hugo 內容模板（參考 [Commands](README.md#commands)）
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── assets/ - 主題的 CSS/JS 與 Tailwind 輸出
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;│ ├── css/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;│ └── js/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── content/ - Hugo 會渲染的 Markdown 文章/頁面
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── data/ - 提供 layouts 使用的資料
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── layouts/ - 自訂 Hugo 佈局
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── scripts/ - 工具，例如 `notion-sync.py`（連回 [Technologies](README.md#technologies)）
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── static/ - 原封不動複製到 `public/` 的靜態資源
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── themes/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;│ └── minimal-black/ - Minimal Black 主題（詳見 [Theme](README.md#theme)）
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;├── .github/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;│ └── workflows/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;│ └── hugo.yml - GitHub Actions 工作流程（參照 [Deployment](README.md#deployment)）
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;└── hugo.toml - Hugo 設定（baseURL、params、menu）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="mb-collapse-overlay"&gt;
 &lt;button class="mb-expand-trigger"&gt;
 &lt;i class="fas fa-chevron-down"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
 &lt;span&gt;Click to expand&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;script&gt;
(function() {
 'use strict';
 
 const codeblock = document.getElementById('cb-5feceb66');
 if (!codeblock) return;

 const copyBtn = codeblock.querySelector('.mb-copy-btn');
 const collapseBtn = codeblock.querySelector('.mb-collapse-btn');
 const content = codeblock.querySelector('.mb-codeblock-content');
 const overlay = codeblock.querySelector('.mb-collapse-overlay');
 const expandTrigger = overlay?.querySelector('.mb-expand-trigger');

 
 
 
 if (copyBtn) {
 copyBtn.addEventListener('click', async function() {
 let codeText = '';

 
 const codeCell = codeblock.querySelector('.lntd:last-child code');
 if (codeCell) {
 codeText = codeCell.textContent || codeCell.innerText || '';
 } else {
 
 const codeEl = codeblock.querySelector('pre code');
 codeText = codeEl ? (codeEl.textContent || codeEl.innerText || '') : '';
 }

 try {
 await navigator.clipboard.writeText(codeText.trim());
 
 
 const originalHTML = copyBtn.innerHTML;
 copyBtn.innerHTML = '&lt;i class="fas fa-check"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;Copied!&lt;/span&gt;';
 copyBtn.classList.add('mb-btn-success');
 
 setTimeout(() =&gt; {
 copyBtn.innerHTML = originalHTML;
 copyBtn.classList.remove('mb-btn-success');
 }, 2000);
 } catch (err) {
 console.error('Failed to copy code:', err);
 
 
 const textArea = document.createElement('textarea');
 textArea.value = codeText.trim();
 textArea.style.position = 'fixed';
 textArea.style.opacity = '0';
 document.body.appendChild(textArea);
 textArea.select();
 
 try {
 document.execCommand('copy');
 copyBtn.innerHTML = '&lt;i class="fas fa-check"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;Copied!&lt;/span&gt;';
 setTimeout(() =&gt; {
 copyBtn.innerHTML = '&lt;i class="fas fa-copy"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;Copy&lt;/span&gt;';
 }, 2000);
 } catch (fallbackErr) {
 console.error('Fallback copy failed:', fallbackErr);
 }
 
 document.body.removeChild(textArea);
 }
 });
 }

 
 
 
 if (collapseBtn &amp;&amp; content &amp;&amp; overlay) {
 const collapsedHeight = 200 ;
 
 function toggleCollapse() {
 const isCollapsed = content.dataset.state === 'collapsed';
 
 if (isCollapsed) {
 
 content.style.maxHeight = '';
 content.style.overflow = '';
 content.dataset.state = 'expanded';
 overlay.style.display = 'none';
 collapseBtn.innerHTML = '&lt;i class="fas fa-compress-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;Collapse&lt;/span&gt;';
 collapseBtn.dataset.collapsed = 'false';
 } else {
 
 content.style.maxHeight = collapsedHeight + 'px';
 content.style.overflow = 'hidden';
 content.dataset.state = 'collapsed';
 overlay.style.display = 'flex';
 collapseBtn.innerHTML = '&lt;i class="fas fa-expand-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;Expand&lt;/span&gt;';
 collapseBtn.dataset.collapsed = 'true';
 }
 }

 
 if ('expanded' === 'collapsed') {
 content.dataset.state = 'collapsed';
 overlay.style.display = 'flex';
 collapseBtn.innerHTML = '&lt;i class="fas fa-expand-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;Expand&lt;/span&gt;';
 collapseBtn.dataset.collapsed = 'true';
 }

 collapseBtn.addEventListener('click', toggleCollapse);
 
 if (expandTrigger) {
 expandTrigger.addEventListener('click', toggleCollapse);
 }
 }
})();
&lt;/script&gt;

